FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /app
COPY pom.xml ./
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/analytics-dashboard"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java analytics dashboard service"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache curl fontconfig ttf-dejavu && \
    curl -fsSL https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem -o /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem && \
    curl -fsSL https://dl.cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt.pem -o /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem && \
    keytool -importcert -alias aws-rds-root -file /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -importcert -alias azure-digicert-root -file /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/aws-rds-ca.pem /tmp/azure-digicert-ca.pem && \
    addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -u 1001 -G app -D app && \
    chown -R app:app /app

COPY --from=builder --chown=app:app /app/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
